title: Ep 47: 2021 Judgies Draft-a-Thon
description:
Today's proceedings:  A mom who can't stay off of TikTok, a college student underestimating the power of Ambien, and a coworker who can (?) speak multiple languages!  We also do the first annual Judgies Draftathon where we select our favorite Subreddits from the past year!
